T16TD4377E:300b-1: a'arya bha dra tsarya pra ni dh'a na r'a dza /
T16TD4377E:300b-3: 'phags pa bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam gyi rgyal po //
T16TD4377E:300b-4: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4377E:300b-5: ji snyed su dag phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten na //
T16TD4377E:300b-6: dus gsum gshegs pa mi yi seng ge kun //
T16TD4377E:300b-7: bdag gis ma lus de dag thams cad la //
T16TD4377E:300b-8: lus dang ngag yid dang bas phyag bgyi'o //
T16TD4377E:300b-9: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam stobs dag gis //
T16TD4377E:300b-10: rgyal ba thams cad yid kyi mngon sum du //
T16TD4377E:300b-11: zhing gi rdul snyed lus rab btud pa yis //
T16TD4377E:300b-12: rgyal ba kun la rab tu phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4377E:300b-13: rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed sangs rgyas rnams //
T16TD4377E:300b-14: sangs rgyas sras kyi dbus na bzhugs pa dag / de ltar chos kyi dbyings rnams ma lus pa //
T16TD4377E:300b-15: thams cad rgyal ba dag gis gang bar mos //
T16TD4377E:300b-16: de dag bsngags pa mi zad rgya mtsho rnams //
T16TD4377E:300b-17: dbyangs kyi yan lag rgya mtsho'i sgra kun gyis //
T16TD4377E:300b-18: rgyal ba kun gyi yon tan rab brjod cing //
T16TD4377E:300b-19: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad bdag gis bstod //
T16TD4377E:300b-20: me tog dam pa phreng ba dam pa dang /
T16TD4377E:300b-21: sil snyan rnams dang byug pa gdugs mchog dang /
T16TD4377E:300b-22: mar me mchog dang bdug spos dam pa yis //
T16TD4377E:300b-23: rgyal ba de dag la ni mchod par bgyi //
T16TD4377E:300b-24: na bza' dam pa rnams dang dri mchog dang //
T16TD4377E:300b-25: phye ma phur ma ri rab mnyam pa dang /
T16TD4377E:300b-26: bkod pa khyad par 'phags pa'i mchog kun gyis //
T16TD4377E:300b-27: rgyal ba de dag la ni mchod par bgyi //
T16TD4377E:300b-28: mchod pa gang rnams bla med rgya che ba //
T16TD4377E:300b-29: de dag rgyal ba thams cad la yang mos //
T16TD4377E:300b-30: bzang po spyod la dad pa'i stobs dag gis //
T16TD4377E:300b-31: rgyal ba kun la phyag 'tshal mchod par bgyi //
T16TD4377E:300b-32: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug dbang gis ni //
T16TD4377E:300b-33: lus dang ngag dang de bzhin yid kyis kyang //
T16TD4377E:300b-34: sdig pa bdag gis bgyis pa ci mchis pa //
T16TD4377E:300b-35: de dag thams cad bdag gis so sor bshags //
T16TD4377E:300b-36: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba kun dang sangs rgyas sras //
T16TD4377E:300b-37: rang rgyal rnams dang slob dang mi slob dang //
T16TD4377E:300b-38: 'gro ba kun gyi bsod nams gang la yang //
T16TD4377E:300b-39: de dag kun gyi rjes su bdag yi rang //
T16TD4377E:301a-2: byang chub rim par sangs rgyas ma chags brnyes //
T16TD4377E:301a-3: mgon po de dag bdag gis thams cad la //
T16TD4377E:301a-4: 'khor lo bla na med pa bskor bar bskul //
T16TD4377E:301a-5: mya ngan 'da' ston gang bzhed de dag la //
T16TD4377E:301a-6: 'gro ba kun la phan zhing bde ba'i phyir //
T16TD4377E:301a-7: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed bzhugs par yang //
T16TD4377E:301a-8: bdag gis thal mo rab sbyar gsol bar bgyi //
T16TD4377E:301a-9: phyag 'tshal ba dang mchod cing bshags pa dang //
T16TD4377E:301a-10: rjes su yi rang bskul zhing gsol ba yi //
T16TD4377E:301a-11: dge ba cung zad bdag gis ci bsags pa //
T16TD4377E:301a-12: thams cad bdag gis byang chub phyir bsngo'o /
T16TD4377E:301a-14: // /'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams dang phyogs bcu yi //
T16TD4377E:301a-15: 'jig rten dag na gang bzhugs mchod par gyur //
T16TD4377E:301a-16: gang yang ma byon de dag rab myur bar //
T16TD4377E:301a-17: bsam rdzogs byang chub rim par sangs rgyas spyon //
T16TD4377E:301a-18: phyogs bcu ga la'i zhing rnams ji snyed pa //
T16TD4377E:301a-19: de dag rgya cher yongs su dag par gyur //
T16TD4377E:301a-20: byang chub shing dbang drung gshegs rgyal ba dang //
T16TD4377E:301a-21: sangs rgyas sras kyis rab tu gang bar shog / phyogs bcu'i sems can gang rnams ji snyed pa //
T16TD4377E:301a-22: de dag rtag tu nad med bde bar gyur //
T16TD4377E:301a-23: 'gro ba kun gyi chos kyi don rnams ni //
T16TD4377E:301a-24: mthun par gyur cing re ba'ang 'grub par shog / byang chub spyod pa dag ni bdag spyod cing //
T16TD4377E:301a-25: 'gro ba kun tu skye ba dran par gyur //
T16TD4377E:301a-26: tshe rabs kun tu 'chi 'pho skye ba na //
T16TD4377E:301a-27: rtag tu bdag ni rab tu 'byung bar shog / rgyal ba kun gyi rjes su slob gyur te //
T16TD4377E:301a-28: bzang po spyod pa yongs su rdzogs byed cing //
T16TD4377E:301a-29: tshul khrims spyod pa dri med yong dag pa //
T16TD4377E:301a-30: rtag tu ma nyams skyon med spyod par shog / lha yi skad dang klu dang gnod sbyin skad //
T16TD4377E:301a-31: grul bum dag dang mi yi skad rnams dang //
T16TD4377E:301a-32: 'gro ba kun gyi sgra rnams ji tsam par //
T16TD4377E:301a-33: thams cad skad du bdag gis chos bstan to //
T16TD4377E:301a-34: des shing pha rol phyin la rab brtson te //
T16TD4377E:301a-35: byang chub sems ni nam yang brjed ma gyur //
T16TD4377E:301a-36: sdig pa gang rnams sgrib par gyur pa dag / de dag ma lus yongs su byang bar shog / las dang nyon mongs bdud kyi las rnams las //
T16TD4377E:301b-0: grol zhing 'jig rten 'gro @301b ba rnams su yang //
T16TD4377E:301b-1: ji ltar padmo chus mi chags pa bzhin //
T16TD4377E:301b-2: nyi zla nam mkhar thogs pa med ltar spyad //
T16TD4377E:301b-3: zhing gi khyon dang phyogs rnams ji tsam par //
T16TD4377E:301b-4: ngan song sdug bsngal rab tu zhi bar byed //
T16TD4377E:301b-5: bde ba dag la 'gro ba kun 'god cing //
T16TD4377E:301b-6: 'gro ba thams cad la ni phan par spyad //
T16TD4377E:301b-7: byang chub spyod pa yongs su rdzogs byed cing //
T16TD4377E:301b-8: sems can dag gi spyod dang mthun par 'jug / bzang po spyod pa dag ni rab ston cing //
T16TD4377E:301b-9: ma 'ongs bskal ba kun tu spyod par gyur //
T16TD4377E:301b-10: bdag gi spyod dang mtshungs par gang spyod pa //
T16TD4377E:301b-11: de dag dang ni rtag tu 'grogs par shog / lus dang ngag rnams dang ni sems kyis kyang //
T16TD4377E:301b-12: spyod pa dag dang smon lam gcig tu spyad //
T16TD4377E:301b-13: bdag la phan par 'dod pa'i grogs po dag / bzang po spyod pa rab tu ston pa rnams //
T16TD4377E:301b-14: de dag dang yang rtag tu phrad par shog / de dag bdag gis nam yang yid mid byung //
T16TD4377E:301b-15: sangs rgyas rgyas sras kyis bskor ba'i mgon po rnams //
T16TD4377E:301b-16: mngon sum rtag tu bdag gis rgyal ba blta //
T16TD4377E:301b-17: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu mi skyo bar //
T16TD4377E:301b-18: de dag la yang mchod pa rgya cher bgyi //
T16TD4377E:301b-19: rgyal ba rnams kyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin cing //
T16TD4377E:301b-20: byang chub spyod pa kun tu snang bar byed //
T16TD4377E:301b-21: bzang po spyod pa rnam par sbyong ba yang //
T16TD4377E:301b-22: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu spyad par bgyi //
T16TD4377E:301b-23: srid pa thams cad du yang 'khor ba na //
T16TD4377E:301b-24: bsod nams ye shes dag ni mi zad rnyed //
T16TD4377E:301b-25: thabs dang shes rab ting 'dzin rnam thar dang //
T16TD4377E:301b-26: yon tan kun gyi mi zad mdzod du gyur //
T16TD4377E:301b-27: rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed zhing rnams te //
T16TD4377E:301b-28: zhing der bsam gyis mi khyab sangs rgyas rnams //
T16TD4377E:301b-29: sangs rgyas sras kyi dbus na bzhugs pa la //
T16TD4377E:301b-30: byang chub spyad pa spyod cing blta bar bgyi //
T16TD4377E:301b-31: de ltar ma lus thams cad phyogs su yang //
T16TD4377E:301b-32: skra tsam khyon la dus gsum tshad snyed kyi //
T16TD4377E:301b-33: sangs rgyas rgya mtsho zhing rnams rgya mtsho dang //
T16TD4377E:301b-34: bskal ba rgya mtshor spyod cing rab tu 'jug / gsung gcig yan lag rgya mtsho'i sgra kun gyis //
T16TD4377E:301b-35: rgyal ba kun dbyangs yan lag rnam dag pa //
T16TD4377E:301b-36: 'gro ba kun gyi bsam pa ji bzhin dbyangs //
T16TD4377E:301b-37: sangs rgyas gsung la rtag tu 'jug par bgyi //
T16TD4377E:302a-0: dus gsum gshegs pa'i rgyal ba @302a * //
T16TD4377E:302a-1: thams cad dag /'khor lo'i tshul rnams rab tu bskor ba yi //
T16TD4377E:302a-2: de dag gi yang gsung dbyangs mi zad la //
T16TD4377E:302a-3: blo yi stobs kyis bdag kyang rab tu 'jug / ma 'ongs bskal pa thams cad 'jug par yang //
T16TD4377E:302a-4: skad cig gcig gis bdag kyang 'jug par bgyi //
T16TD4377E:302a-5: gang yang bskal pa dus gsum tshad de dag / skad cig cha shas kyis ni zhugs par spyad //
T16TD4377E:302a-6: dus gsum gshegs pa mi yi seng ge gang //
T16TD4377E:302a-7: de dag skad cig gcig la bdag gis blta //
T16TD4377E:302a-8: rtag tu de dag gi ni spyod yul la //
T16TD4377E:302a-9: sgyu mar gyur pa'i rnam thar stobs kyis 'jug / gang yang dus gsum dag gi zhing bkod pa //
T16TD4377E:302a-10: de dag rdul gcig steng du mngon par bsgrub //
T16TD4377E:302a-11: de ltar ma lus phyogs rnams thams cad du //
T16TD4377E:302a-12: rgyal ba dag gi zhing rnams bkod la 'jug / gang yang ma byon 'jig rten sgron ma rnams //
T16TD4377E:302a-13: de dag rim par 'tshang rgya 'khor lo bskor//
T16TD4377E:302a-14: mya ngan 'das pa rab tu zhi mtha' ston //
T16TD4377E:302a-15: mgon po kun gyi drung du bdag mchi'o //
T16TD4377E:302a-16: kun du myur ba'i rdzu 'phrul stobs rnams dang //
T16TD4377E:302a-17: kun nas sgo yi theg pa'i stobs dag dang //
T16TD4377E:302a-18: kun tu yon tan spyod pa'i stobs rnams dang //
T16TD4377E:302a-19: kun tu khyab pa byams pa dag gi stobs //
T16TD4377E:302a-20: kun nas dge ba'i bsod nams stobs dag dang //
T16TD4377E:302a-21: chags pa med par gyur ba'i ye shes stobs //
T16TD4377E:302a-22: shes rab thabs dang ting 'dzin stobs dag gis //
T16TD4377E:302a-23: byang chub stobs rnams yang dag sgrub par byed //
T16TD4377E:302a-24: las kyi stobs rnams yongs su dag byed cing //
T16TD4377E:302a-25: nyon mongs stobs rnams kun tu 'joms par byed //
T16TD4377E:302a-26: bdud kyi stobs rnams stobs med rab byed cing //
T16TD4377E:302a-27: bzang po spyod pa'i stobs ni rdzogs par bgyi //
T16TD4377E:302a-28: zhing rnams rgya mtsho rnam par dag byed cing //
T16TD4377E:302a-29: sems can rgya mtsho dag ni rnam par dgrol //
T16TD4377E:302a-30: chos rnams rgya mtsho rab tu mthong byed cing //
T16TD4377E:302a-31: ye shes rgya mtsho rab tu rtogs par byed //
T16TD4377E:302a-32: spyod pa rgya mtsho rnam par dag byed cing //
T16TD4377E:302a-33: smon lam rgya mtsho yongs su rdzogs par byed //
T16TD4377E:302a-34: sangs rgyas rgya mtsho rab tu mchod byed cing //
T16TD4377E:302a-35: bskal pa rgya mtshor mi skyo spyad par bgyi //
T16TD4377E:302b-0: gang yang dus gsum @302b gshegs pa rgyal ba yi //
T16TD4377E:302b-1: byang chub spyod pa'i smon lam bye brag rnams //
T16TD4377E:302b-2: bzang po spyod pa'i byang chub sangs rgyas nas //
T16TD4377E:302b-3: de kun bdag gis ma lus rdzogs par bgyi //
T16TD4377E:302b-4: rgyal ba kun gyi sras kyi thu bo pa //
T16TD4377E:302b-5: gang gi ming ni kun tu bzang zhes bya //
T16TD4377E:302b-6: mkhas pa de dang mtshungs par spyad pa'i phyir //
T16TD4377E:302b-7: dge ba 'di dag thams cad rab tu bsngo //
T16TD4377E:302b-8: lus dang ngag dang yid kyang rnam dag cing //
T16TD4377E:302b-9: spyod pa rnam dag zhing rnams yongs dag dang //
T16TD4377E:302b-10: bsngo ba bzang po mkhas pa ci 'dra ba //
T16TD4377E:302b-11: de 'drar bdag kyang de dang mtshungs par shog / kun nas dge ba bzang po spyad pa'i phyir //
T16TD4377E:302b-12: 'jam dpal gyi ni smon lam spyad par bgyi //
T16TD4377E:302b-13: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu mi skyo bar //
T16TD4377E:302b-14: de yi bya ba ma lus rdzogs par bgyi //
T16TD4377E:302b-15: spyod pa dag ni tshad yod ma gyur cig / yon tan rnams kyang tshad bzung med par shog / spyod pa tshad med pa la gnas nas kyang//
T16TD4377E:302b-16: de dag 'phrul pa thams cad 'tshal bar bgyi //
T16TD4377E:302b-17: nam mkha'i mthar thug gyur pa ji tsam par //
T16TD4377E:302b-18: sems can ma lus mtha' yang de bzhin te //
T16TD4377E:302b-19: ji tsam las dang nyon mongs mthar gyur pa //
T16TD4377E:302b-20: bdag gi smon lam mtha' yang de tsam mo //
T16TD4377E:302b-21: gang yang phyogs bcu'i zhing rnams mtha' yas pa //
T16TD4377E:302b-22: rin chen brgyan te rgyal ba rnams la phul //
T16TD4377E:302b-23: lha dang mi yi bde ba'i mchog rnams kyang //
T16TD4377E:302b-24: zhing gi rdul snyed bskal par phul ba bas //
T16TD4377E:302b-25: gang gis bsngo ba'i rgyal po 'di thos nas //
T16TD4377E:302b-26: byang chub mchog gi rjes su rab mos shing //
T16TD4377E:302b-27: lan cig tsam yang dad pa bskyed pa na //
T16TD4377E:302b-28: bsod nams dam pa'i mchog tu 'di 'gyur ro //
T16TD4377E:302b-29: gang gis bzang spyod smon lam 'di btab pas //
T16TD4377E:302b-30: des ni ngan song thams cad spang bar 'gyur //
T16TD4377E:302b-31: des ni grogs po ngan pa spangs pa yin //
T16TD4377E:302b-32: snang ba mtha' yas de yang des myur mthong //
T16TD4377E:302b-33: de dag rnyed pa rab rnyed bde bar 'tsho //
T16TD4377E:302b-34: mi tshe 'dir yang de dag legs par 'ong //
T16TD4377E:302b-35: kun tu bzang po de yang ci 'dra bar //
T16TD4377E:302b-36: de dag ring por mi thogs de bzhin 'gyur //
T16TD4377E:302b-37: mtshams med lnga po dag gi sdig pa rnams //
T16TD4377E:303a-0: gang gi mi shes dbang gis byas pa dag / de yis bzang po spyod pa 'di @303a * //
T16TD4377E:303a-2: myur du ma las yongs su byang bar 'gyur //
T16TD4377E:303a-3: ye shes dang ni gzugs dang mtshan rnams dang //
T16TD4377E:303a-4: rigs dang kha dog rnams dang ldan par 'gyur //
T16TD4377E:303a-5: bdud dang mu stegs mang pos de mi thub //
T16TD4377E:303a-6: 'jig rten gsum po kun na'ang mchod par 'gyur //
T16TD4377E:303a-7: byang chub shang dbang drung du de myur 'gro //
T16TD4377E:303a-8: song nas sems can phan phyir der 'dug ste //
T16TD4377E:303a-9: byang chub sangs rgyas 'khor lo rab tu bskor //
T16TD4377E:303a-10: bdud rnams sde dang bcas pa thams cad btul //
T16TD4377E:303a-11: gang yang bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam 'di //
T16TD4377E:303a-12: 'chang ba dang ni ston tam klog pa yi //
T16TD4377E:303a-13: de yi rnam par smin pa sangs rgyas mkhyen //
T16TD4377E:303a-14: byang chub mchog la som nyi ma byed cig /'jam dpal ji ltar mkhyen cing dpa' ba dang //
T16TD4377E:303a-15: kun tu bzang po de yang de bzhin te //
T16TD4377E:303a-16: de dag kun gyi rjes su bdag slob cing //
T16TD4377E:303a-17: dge ba 'di dag thams cad rab tu bsngo //
T16TD4377E:303a-18: dus gsum gshegs pa rgyal ba thams cad kyis //
T16TD4377E:303a-19: bsngo ba gang la mchog tu bsngags pa des //
T16TD4377E:303a-20: bdag gi dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di kun kyang //
T16TD4377E:303a-21: bzang po spyod phyir rab tu bsngo bar bgyi //
T16TD4377E:303a-22: bdag ni 'chi ba'i dus byed gyur pa na //
T16TD4377E:303a-23: sgrib pa thams cad dag ni phyir bsal te //
T16TD4377E:303a-24: mngon sum snang ba mtha' yas de mthong nas //
T16TD4377E:303a-25: bde ba can gyi zhing der rab tu 'gro //
T16TD4377E:303a-26: der song nas ni smon lam 'di dag kyang //
T16TD4377E:303a-27: thams cad ma lus mngon du 'gyur bar shog / de dag ma lus bdag gis yongs su bkang //
T16TD4377E:303a-28: 'jig rten ji srid sems can phan par bgyi //
T16TD4377E:303a-29: rgyal ba'i dkyil sa khor bzang zhing dga' ba der //
T16TD4377E:303a-30: padmo dam pa shin tu mdzes las skyes //
T16TD4377E:303a-31: snang ba mtha' yas rgyal bas mngon sum du //
T16TD4377E:303a-32: yung bstan pa yang bdag gis der thob shog / der ni bdag gis lung bstan rab thob nas //
T16TD4377E:303a-33: sprul pa mang po bye ba phrag brgya yis //
T16TD4377E:303a-34: blo yi stobs kyis phyogs bcu rnams su yang //
T16TD4377E:303a-35: sems can rnams la phan pa mang po bgyi //
T16TD4377E:303a-36: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam bton pa yi //
T16TD4377E:303a-37: dge ba cung zad bdag gis ci bsags pa //
T16TD4377E:303a-38: des ni 'gro ba'i smon lam dge ba rnams //
T16TD4377E:303b-0: skad cig gcig gis thams cad 'byor ba @303b shog / gang yang bzang po spyod pa 'di bsngos pas //
T16TD4377E:303b-1: bsod nams mtha' yas dam pa gang thob des //
T16TD4377E:303b-2: 'gro ba sdug bsngal chu bor bying ba rnams //
T16TD4377E:303b-3: 'od dpag med pa'i gnas rab thob par shog / smon lam rgyal po 'di dag mchog gi gtso //
T16TD4377E:303b-4: mtha' yas 'gro ba kun la phan byed cing //
T16TD4377E:303b-5: kun tu bzang pos brgyan pa'i gzhung grub ste //
T16TD4377E:303b-6: ngan song gnas rnams ma lus stongs par shog /'phags pa bzang po sbyong ba'i smon lam gyi rgyal po rdzogs so /
T16TD4377E:303b-8: // /'di byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod kyi nang tshan phal po che'i sdong po brgyan pa zhes bya ba 'chos kyi rnam grangs nor bzang gis dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsnyan bkur ba'i spyod pa phyogs gcig pa'i le'u las phyung ba'o//
